        "type": "stat_block",
        "subtype": "equipment",
        "text": "You create a snare that releases a dense cloud of smoke when a creature enters the square, filling a specified area. All creatures within that area are concealed, and all other creatures are concealed to them. The smoke lasts for 1 minute or until dispersed by a strong wind.",
